---------------------------------

Underworld I is the first digital triptych made inseparable via blockchain. Inspired by the ingenuity of three-panel altarpieces held together with hinges, we have leveraged the blockchain to weld ours together and achieve the same level of provenance. Though each of the three pieces is a separate non-fungible token, their smart contractb�s laws bind them eternally. Transfer any in the set, and the other two force themselves to take the same fate.

For collectors, rest assured that buying any one of the three pieces (Hades, Cerberus, Persephone) will instantly transfer all three to your wallet upon confirmation. And be warned, selling any of the three will cause all three to leave your wallet. On-chain metadata holds gallery display notes for each piece.
